                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9909" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1496</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1192 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">溯本求源：W公司远期锁汇的智能改革与探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tracing the origins: Intelligent transformation and exploration of forward hedging at Company W</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张雪娇，段旭萌，赵青扬，韩玉玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">W公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇率风险；远期外汇交易；数智化转型；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Exchange rate risk; Forward exchange transaction; Digital Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外贸企业往往因汇率波动而面临外汇风险，远期锁汇具有交易规模较大、交割日灵活的特点，被大多数外贸企业用以规避外汇风险。那么，如何更好地管理远期锁汇交易以尽可能减少外汇风险呢？本案例以外贸企业W公司为例，聚焦其远期锁汇从“Excel手动记录”到“资金平台”线上管理的智能改革过程，从申请锁汇、进行锁汇、到期交割并确认流水等远期锁汇环节入手，描述了W公司申请锁汇时的信息不透明问题，远期锁汇时的“Excel手动记录”导致信息不准确和统计繁琐问题，以及到期交割时的收款和交割订单难以匹配等问题，复现了W公司通过建立资金平台与打通数据孤岛，实现锁汇信息透明、锁汇效率提高、锁汇全流程打通的远期锁汇智能改革过程。本案例旨在引导学员思考外贸企业如何更好地进行远期外汇管理，以有效降低汇率风险。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Foreign trade enterprises often face foreign exchange risks due to exchange rate fluctuations. Forward foreign exchange transactions, characterized by large transaction volumes and flexible settlement dates, are widely adopted by most foreign trade companies to hedge against such risks. So, how can forward foreign exchange transactions be better managed to minimize foreign exchange risks? This case study takes W Company, a foreign trade enterprise, as an example. Focusing on its intelligent transformation from “manual Excel recording” to online management via a “funding platform” for forward foreign exchange transactions, it examines key stages—applying for forward foreign exchange positions, executing contracts, settlement upon maturity, and transaction verification. The case describes issues such as lack of transparency during application, inaccurate data and cumbersome statistics caused by manual Excel tracking, and difficulties in reconciling payments with settlement orders upon maturity. It then details how W Company achieved transparent foreign exchange hedging information, improved efficiency, and end-to-end process integration by establishing a funding platform and breaking down data silos. The case aims to guide students in contemplating how foreign trade enterprises can enhance forward foreign exchange management to effectively mitigate exchange rate risks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《国际金融》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇率风险的分类；汇率风险管理的整体性原则；汇率波动的影响因素；远期结汇业务流程优化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
